###############################################################################
# Azure AI Foundry Agent Metadata API Tests
#
# VS Code REST Client 格式 — 点击每个请求上方的 "Send Request" 即可运行
#
# 前置：
#   1. 安装 VS Code 扩展 "REST Client" (humao.rest-client)
#   2. 在同目录创建 .env 文件（已被 .gitignore 忽略），内容如下：
#      AZURE_FOUNDRY_ENDPOINT=https://your-resource.services.ai.azure.com
#      AZURE_FOUNDRY_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
#      AZURE_FOUNDRY_PROJECT=your-project-name
#
# 使用：按序号从上到下依次点击 "Send Request" 运行
###############################################################################

### ===== 配置区（从 .env 读取，无需硬编码） =====

@baseEndpoint = {{$dotenv AZURE_FOUNDRY_ENDPOINT}}
@projectName = {{$dotenv AZURE_FOUNDRY_PROJECT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv AZURE_FOUNDRY_API_KEY}}
@apiVersion = 2025-05-01

### ===== 动态变量 =====
@projectUrl = {{baseEndpoint}}/api/projects/{{projectName}}

###############################################################################
# 测试 1：Metadata 基本读写 Round-Trip
###############################################################################

### 1a. 创建 Agent（带 metadata）
# @name createBasic
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-basic/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "You are a test agent for metadata API verification."
  },
  "description": "Postman metadata test agent",
  "metadata": {
    "custom-key-1": "hello",
    "custom-key-2": "world",
    "number-as-string": "42"
  }
}

### 1b. 读回 Agent（验证 metadata）
# 检查 versions.latest.metadata 中的 key-value 是否一致
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-basic?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 1c. 删除 Agent（清理）
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-basic?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}


###############################################################################
# 测试 2：512 字符限制验证
###############################################################################

### 2a. 512 字符 — 应该成功 ✅
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-512ok/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test 512 char limit."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "test-key": ""
  }
}

### 2a-cleanup. 删除 512 测试 Agent
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-512ok?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 2b. 513 字符 — 应该失败 ❌（错误消息含 "512"）
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-513fail/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test 513 char limit."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "test-key": ""
  }
}

### 2c. 1024 字符 — 应该失败 ❌
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-1024/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test 1024 char limit."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "test-key": ""
  }
}


###############################################################################
# 测试 3：Voice Live Metadata 格式
###############################################################################

### 3a. 精简格式（省略默认值）— 应该成功 ✅ (167 chars)
# 创建后可去 AI Foundry Portal 查看 Voice mode 是否显示为 ON
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-vl-compact/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "You are a Voice Live test agent."
  },
  "description": "VL Postman Test Agent",
  "metadata": {
    "microsoft.voice-live.enabled": "true",
    "microsoft.voice-live.configuration": "{\"session\":{\"voice\":{\"name\":\"zh-CN-XiaoxiaoMultilingualNeural\"},\"turnDetection\":{\"type\":\"azure_semantic_vad\"},\"avatar\":{\"character\":\"lisa\",\"style\":\"casual-sitting\"}}}",
    "description": "VL Test Agent",
    "modified_at": "1712700000"
  }
}

### 3b. 读回 VL Agent（验证 config round-trip）
# 检查 microsoft.voice-live.enabled = "true"
# 检查 microsoft.voice-live.configuration 解析后 avatar.character = "lisa"
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-vl-compact?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 3c. 完整格式（含所有 null 和默认值）— 应该失败 ❌ (~607 chars > 512)
# 如果成功 → Azure 已放宽 512 限制，可以恢复完整格式
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-vl-full/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test full VL config."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "microsoft.voice-live.enabled": "true",
    "microsoft.voice-live.configuration": "{\"session\":{\"voice\":{\"name\":\"zh-CN-XiaoxiaoMultilingualNeural\",\"type\":\"azure-standard\",\"temperature\":0.8,\"rate\":\"1.0\",\"isHdVoice\":false},\"inputAudioTranscription\":{\"model\":\"azure-speech\",\"language\":\"auto-detect\"},\"turnDetection\":{\"type\":\"azure_semantic_vad\",\"endOfUtteranceDetection\":null,\"removeFillerWords\":true},\"inputAudioNoiseReduction\":null,\"inputAudioEchoCancellation\":null,\"fillerResponse\":null,\"avatar\":{\"character\":\"lisa\",\"style\":\"casual-sitting\",\"customized\":false},\"proactiveEngagement\":false}}"
  }
}

### 3d. 清理 VL 测试 Agents
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-vl-compact?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 3e. 清理完整格式 Agent（如果创建成功了的话）
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-vl-full?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}


###############################################################################
# 测试 4：版本号追踪
###############################################################################

### 4a. 创建 Agent v1
# @name createV1
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-version/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Version 1 instructions."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "step": "1"
  }
}

### 4b. 创建 v2（改 instructions + metadata）— version 应该 > v1
# @name createV2
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-version/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Version 2 — updated instructions."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "step": "2",
    "extra": "data"
  }
}

### 4c. 创建 v3（只改 metadata）— version 应该 > v2
# @name createV3
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-version/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Version 2 — updated instructions."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "step": "3",
    "extra": "more-data",
    "new-key": "appears"
  }
}

### 4d. GET 最新版本 — 验证 metadata 是 v3 的
# 注意：metadata 在 versions.latest.metadata 路径下
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-version?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 4e. 清理
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-version?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}


###############################################################################
# 测试 5：错误用例
###############################################################################

### 5a. 缺少 api-key — 应该 401
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/nonexistent-agent?api-version={{apiVersion}}

### 5b. 错误的 api-key — 应该 401
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/nonexistent-agent?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: wrong-key-12345

### 5c. 不存在的 Agent — 应该 404
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/definitely-nonexistent-agent-xyz?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 5d. 缺少 definition 字段 — 应该 400/422
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-nodef/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "metadata": {
    "test-key": "no definition provided"
  }
}


###############################################################################
# 测试 6：Metadata 合并行为（Replace vs Merge）
###############################################################################

### 6a. 创建 v1（key-a + key-b）
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-merge/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test merge behavior."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "key-a": "alpha",
    "key-b": "beta"
  }
}

### 6b. 创建 v2（只传 key-c）— 看 key-a/key-b 是否保留
POST {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-merge/versions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definition": {
    "type": "prompt",
    "model": "gpt-4o",
    "instructions": "Test merge behavior."
  },
  "metadata": {
    "key-c": "gamma"
  }
}

### 6c. 读回 — 检查 metadata 是 replace 还是 merge
# 如果只有 key-c → replace 模式（每个版本独立 metadata）
# 如果有 key-a + key-b + key-c → merge 模式
GET {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-merge?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 6d. 清理
DELETE {{projectUrl}}/agents/postman-test-merge?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
